{"title_page": "Muhyiddin Yassin", "text_new": "{{short description|Prime Minister of Malaysia}}\n{{Malay name|Muhyiddin|Yassin|note=on}}\n{{EngvarB|date=March 2020}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2020}}\n{{Infobox officeholder\n| honorific-prefix = [[Malay titles#Honorary styles|Yang Amat Berhormat]] [[Malay titles#Federal titles|Tan Sri]] [[Malay titles#State tiles|Dato']]\n| name = Muhyiddin Yassin\n| native_name = {{lang|ms|{{Script|Arab|\u0645\u062d\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064a\u0646 \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u062d\u0645\u062f \u064a\u0633\u0653}}}}\n| honorific-suffix = {{post-nominal|post-noms=[[Order of Loyalty to the Crown of Malaysia#Commander|PSM]] [[Order of the Crown of Johor|SPMJ]] [[Order of Loyalty to Sultan Abdul Halim Mu'adzam Shah|SHMS]] [[List of post-nominal letters (Malacca)|DUNM]] [[List of post-nominal letters (Perak)|SPSA]] [[List of post-nominal letters (Perlis)|SPMP]] [[List of post-nominal letters (Negeri Sembilan)|SUNS]] [[List of post-nominal letters (Sabah)|SPDK]] [[Order of the Star of Hornbill Sarawak#Datuk Patinggi Bintang Kenyalang (D.P.)|DP]] [[Most Exalted Order of the Star of Sarawak#Panglima Negara Bintang Sarawak (P.N.B.S.)|PNBS]] [[Parliament of Malaysia|MP]] [[Member of the Legislative Assembly|MLA]]}}\n| image = TSMY Menteri Dalam Negeri.jpg\n| imagesize = 230px\n| birth_name = Mahiaddin bin Md Yassin<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2018/04/29/muhyiddin-to-ec-use-the-name-he-chose/ |title=Don't spell my name as Mahiaddin, Muhyiddin tells Election Commission|date=29 April 2018 |newspaper=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]]}}</ref>\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=y|1947|5|15}}\n| birth_place = [[Muar (town)|Muar]], Johor, [[Malayan Union]]\n| residence = [[Seri Perdana]], [[Putrajaya]] <br>[[Damansara Heights]], [[Kuala Lumpur]]\n| death_date = [[File:Rat.jpg]]\n| death_place = [[File:Mouse.jpg]]\n| office = 8th [[Prime Minister of Malaysia]]\n| status = \n| monarch = [[Abdullah of Pahang|Abdullah]]\