ja''' (2010)<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=12 October 2019|date=21 April 2010|work=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]]|location= Malaysia |url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/community/2010/04/21/sultan-of-perak-82nd-birthday-honours-list|title=Sultan of Perak 82nd birthday honours list}}</ref>\n* [[File:Coat_of_arms_of_Perlis.svg|30px|link=Perlis]] {{Flag|Perlis}}:\n** [[File:MY-PERL_Order_of_the_Crown_of_Perlis_-_Knight_Grand_Commander_-_SPMP.svg|50px|link=Orders, decorations, and medals of Perlis|Knight Grand Commander of the Order of the Crown of Perlis, the Star of Safi]] Knight Grand Commander of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Perlis|Order of the Crown of Perlis, the Star of Safi]] (SPMP) \u2013 '''Dato' Seri''' (2007)\n* [[File:Coat_of_arms_of_Negeri_Sembilan.svg|20px|link=Negeri Sembilan]] {{Flag|Negeri Sembilan}}:\n** [[File:MY-NEG_Order_of_Loyalty_to_Negeri_Sembilan.svg|50px|link=Orders, decorations, and medals of Negeri Sembilan|Principal Grand Knight of the Order of Loyalty to Negeri Sembilan]] Principal Grand Knight of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Negeri Sembilan|Order of Loyalty to Negeri Sembilan]] (SUNS) \u2013 '''Dato' Seri Utama''' (2010)<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=12 October 2019|date=14 January 2010|work=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]]|location= Malaysia |url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2010/01/14/five-royals-on-negri-sembilan-honours-list|title=Five royals on Negri Sembilan honours list}}</ref>\n* [[File:Coat_of_arms_of_Sabah.svg|20px|link=Sabah]] {{Flag|Sabah}}:\n** [[File:MY-SAB_Order_of_Kinabalu_-_SPDK.svg|50px|link=Order of Kinabalu|Grand Commander of the Order of Kinabalu]] Grand Commander of the [[Order of Kinabalu#Grand Commander|Order of Kinabalu]] (SPDK) \u2013 '''Datuk Seri Panglima''' (2010)<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=12 October 2019|date=3 October 2010|work=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]]|location= Malaysia |url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2010/10/03/dpm-heads-sabah-tyt-honours-list/|title=DPM heads Sabah TYT honours list}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|accessdate=12 October 2019|date=3 October 2010|work=[[Borneo Post]]|url=https://www.theborneopost.com/2010/10/03/muhyiddin-heads-sabah-honours-list/|title=Muhyiddin heads Sabah honours list}}</ref>\n* [[File:Coat_of_arms_of_Sarawak.svg|20px|link=Sarawak]] {{Flag|Sarawak}}:\n** [[File:MY-SAR_Order_of_the_Star_of_Sarawak_-_2_ribbon_PNBS_-JBS-PBS-ABS-BBS.svg|50px|link=Most Exalted Order of the Star of Sarawak|Knight Commander of the Order of the Star of Sarawak]] Knight Commander of the [[Most Exalted Order of the Star of Sarawak#Panglima Negara Bintang Sarawak (P.N.B.S.)|Order of the Star of Sarawak]] (PNBS) \u2013 '''Dato Sri''' (2008)<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=12 October 2019|title=Sarawak Honours List 2008|date=5 November 2008|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/community/2008/11/05/sarawak-honours-list-2008|work=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]]|location= Malaysia }}</ref>\n** [[File:MY-SAR_Order_of_the_Star_of_the_Hornbill_(Bintang_Kenyalang)_-_1._Knight_Grand_Commander_(DP).svg|50px|link=Order of the Star of Hornbill Sarawak|Knight Grand Commander of the Star of Hornbill Sarawak]] Knight Grand Commander of the [[Order of the Star of Hornbill Sarawak#Datuk Patinggi Bintang Kenyalang (D.P.)|Order of the Star of Hornbill Sarawak]] (DP) \u2013 '''Datuk Patinggi''' (2010)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/254225|publisher=[[Malaysiakini]]|language=Malay|date=13 February 2010|title=TPM terima Bintang Kenyalang Sarawak|accessdate=12 October 2019}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n*[[Pagoh (federal constituency)]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n{{Wikiquote|Muhyiddin Yassin}}\n{{commons category-inline|Muhyiddin Yassin}}\n{{Wikiquote-inline}}\n* [http://www.pmo.gov.my/tpm/ Deputy Prime Minister of Malaysia Official Website]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20100201213555/http://www.johordt.gov.my/pmbj/v2/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=5&Itemid=9 Johor Menteri Besar Office|Menteri Besar Biography|Tan Sri Muhyiddin Yassin]\n* [http://www.mykmujohor.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=937&Itemid=53 My KMU Johor|Tan Sri Muhyiddin Yassin]\n* [http://johoreanstudentsociety.blogspot.com/2009/11/biografi-mantan-mantan-menteri-besar.html Johorean Student Society|Persatuan Mahasiswa Anak Johor (PERMAJ)|National University of Malaysia|Universiti Kebangsaan Malaysia (UKM)|Biografi Mantan Menteri Besar Johor]\n\n{{navboxes\n|title= Offices\n|state=collapsed\n|list=\n{{S-start}}\n{{S-off|}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Abdul Ajib Ahmad]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Menteri Besar of Johor]]|years= 1986\u20131995}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Abdul Ghani Othman]]}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Abdul Ghani Othman]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Minister of Youth and Sports (Malaysia)|Minister of Youth and Sports]]|years= 1995\u20131999}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Hishammuddin Hussein]]}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Megat Junid]] Megat Ayob}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Minister of Domestic Trade and Consumer Affairs (Malaysia)|Minister of Domestic Trade and Consumer Affairs]]|years= 1999\u20132004 }}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Shafie Apdal|Mohd Shafie Apdal]]}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Mohd Effendi Norwawi]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Minister of Agriculture and Agro-based Industry (Malaysia)|Minister of Agriculture and Agro-based Industry]]|years= 2004\u20132008}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Mustapa Mohamed]]}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Rafidah Aziz]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Minister of International Trade and Industry (Malaysia)|Minister of International Trade and Industry]]|years= 2008\u20132009}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Mustapa Mohamed]]<br />[[Ong Ka Chuan]]}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Hishammuddin Hussein]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Ministry of Education (Malaysia)|Ministry of Education]]|years= 2009\u20132015}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Mahdzir Khalid]]}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Najib Razak]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Deputy Prime Minister of Malaysia]]|years= 2009\u20132015}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Ahmad Zahid Hamidi]]}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Mahathir Mohamad]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Prime Minister of Malay