ms_of_Malaysia.svg|30px|link=Government of Malaysia]] {{Flag|Malaysia}}:\n** [[File:Order_of_Loyalty_to_the_Crown_of_Malaysia_-_PSM.svg|50px|link=Order of Loyalty to the Crown of Malaysia|Commander of the Order of Loyalty to the Crown of Malaysia]] Commander of the [[Order of Loyalty to the Crown of Malaysia#Commander|Order of Loyalty to the Crown of Malaysia]] (PSM) \u2013 '''Tan Sri''' (1988)<ref name=\":Semakan\">{{cite web|title=Semakan Penerima Darjah Kebesaran, Bintang dan Pingat|url=http://www.istiadat.gov.my/index.php/component/semakanlantikanskp/|publisher=[[Prime Minister's Department (Malaysia)|Prime Minister's Department]]}}</ref>\n* [[File:Coat_of_arms_of_Johor.svg|30px|link=Johor]] {{Flag|Johor}}:\n** [[File:Sultan_Ibrahim_Coronation_Medal_ribbon.gif|50px|link=List of post-nominal letters (Johor)|Sultan Ibrahim Medal]] [[List of post-nominal letters (Johor)|Sultan Ibrahim Medal]] (PIS) (II) (1974)\n** [[File:My-KEL_Order_of_the_Life_of_the_Crown_of_Kelantan_2006.svg|50px|link=List of post-nominal letters (Johor)|Star of Sultan Ismail]] [[List of post-nominal letters (Johor)|Star of Sultan Ismail]] (BSI) (II) (1979)\n** [[File:Most_Honourable_Order_of_the_Crown_of_Johor_-_ribbon_bar.png|50px|link=Order of the Crown of Johor|Companion of the Order of the Crown of Johor]] Companion of the [[Order of the Crown of Johor]] (SMJ) (1980)\n** [[File:Most_Honourable_Order_of_the_Crown_of_Johor_-_ribbon_bar.png|50px|link=Order of the Crown of Johor|Knight Grand Commander of the Order of the Crown of Johor]] Knight Grand Commander of the [[Order of the Crown of Johor]] (SPMJ) \u2013 '''Dato'''' (1991)<ref name=\":Semakan\" />\n* [[File:Coat_of_arms_of_Kedah.svg|30px|link=Kedah]] {{Flag|Kedah}}:\n** [[File:MY-KED_Order_of_Sultan_Abdul_Halim_Muazzam_Shah_-_Grand_Commander_(SHMS).svg|50px|link=Order of Loyalty to Sultan Abdul Halim Mu'adzam Shah|Grand Commander of the Order of Loyalty to Sultan Abdul Halim Mu'adzam Shah]] Grand Commander of the [[Order of Loyalty to 