5 November 2008|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/community/2008/11/05/sarawak-honours-list-2008|work=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]]|location= Malaysia }}</ref>\n** [[File:MY-SAR_Order_of_the_Star_of_the_Hornbill_(Bintang_Kenyalang)_-_1._Knight_Grand_Commander_(DP).svg|50px|link=Order of the Star of Hornbill Sarawak|Knight Grand Commander of the Star of Hornbill Sarawak]] Knight Grand Commander of the [[Order of the Star of Hornbill Sarawak#Datuk Patinggi Bintang Kenyalang (D.P.)|Order of the Star of Hornbill Sarawak]] (DP) \u2013 '''Datuk Patinggi''' (2010)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/254225|publisher=[[Malaysiakini]]|language=Malay|date=13 February 2010|title=TPM terima Bintang Kenyalang Sarawak|accessdate=12 October 2019}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n*[[Pagoh (federal constituency)]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n{{Wikiquote|Muhyiddin Yassin}}\n{{commons category-inline|Muhyiddin Yassin}}\n{{Wikiquote-inline}}\n* [http://www.pmo.gov.my/tpm/ Deputy Prime Minister of Malaysia Official Website]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20100201213555/http://www.johordt.gov.my/pmbj/v2/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=5&Itemid=9 Johor Menteri Besar Office|Menteri Besar Biography|Tan Sri Muhyiddin Yassin]\n* [http://www.mykmujohor.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=937&Itemid=53 My KMU Johor|Tan Sri Muhyiddin Yassin]\n* [http://johoreanstudentsociety.blogspot.com/2009/11/biografi-mantan-mantan-menteri-besar.html Johorean Student Society|Persatuan Mahasiswa Anak Johor (PERMAJ)|National University of Malaysia|Universiti Kebangsaan Malaysia (UKM)|Biografi Mantan Menteri Besar Johor]\n\n{{navboxes\n|title= Offices\n|state=collapsed\n|list=\n{{S-start}}\n{{S-off|}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Abdul Ajib Ahmad]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Menteri Besar of Johor]]|years= 1986\u20131995}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Abdul Ghani Othman]]}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Abdul Ghani Othman]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Minister of Youth and Sports (M